OL,3,CMemorial service for 55 victims of the
OL,4,CManchester Air Disaster, 40 years on
OL,6,FThe service at Manchester Airport
OL,7,Fincluded a minute's silence, held
OL,8,Fannually on 22 August
OL,10,FA remembrance service has been held
OL,11,Ffor those killed in the Manchester Air
OL,12,FDisaster, on its 40th anniversary.
OL,14,F55 people died when a British Airtours
OL,15,FBoeing 737, bound for Corfu, caught
OL,16,Ffire at the city's airport on 22
OL,17,FAugust 1985.
