OL,3,CMemorial service for 55 victims of the
OL,4,CManchester Air Disaster, 40 years on
OL,6,FFlight 28M was on the runway,
OL,7,Fpreparing to take off, when the fire
OL,8,Fbroke out. 131 passengers and six crew
OL,9,Fwere onboard.
OL,11,FThose gathered for today's service
OL,12,Fobserved a minute's silence, which the
OL,13,Fairport holds annually on 22 August.
OL,15,FThey also heard the name of every
OL,16,Fvictim read aloud, with wreaths laid
OL,17,Fat a wooden memorial where the names
OL,18,Fare inscribed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
