OL,3,CMemorial service for 55 victims of the
OL,4,CManchester Air Disaster, 40 years on
OL,6,FThose who survived recall the moment
OL,7,Fpassengers became "hysterical,
OL,8,Fscreaming, and crying" as their plane
OL,9,Ffilled with "thick black, kind of
OL,10,Facrid smoke."
OL,12,FIt triggered worldwide safety changes
OL,13,Fincluding emergency strip lighting in
OL,14,Fcabin aisles, expanded spaces around
OL,15,Fexits and fire-resistant materials in
OL,16,Faircraft seating.
OL,18,FYet one of the post-disaster
OL,19,Frecommendations, smoke hoods for
OL,20,Fpassengers, was not implemented.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
